@startuml
title OpenData System Context
left to right direction
actor Operator
rectangle "OpenData Framework" as App
cloud "Dataset Publishers\nAPIs, files, HTML" as Publishers
database "SQL Server" as DB
folder "Work / Archive / Failed" as FS
rectangle "Credential Provider" as Creds
Operator --> App : CLI
App --> Publishers : HTTPS
App --> Creds : resolve reference
App --> FS : artefacts
App --> DB : JDBC
@enduml
